        <p align="center" class="style1871"><strong><span class="style34"><a href="earlieramericancomposers.htm"></a></span></strong><span class="style146"><a href="earlieramericancomposers.htm"></a></span><span class="style335"><img src="Images/Amy M Beach.jpg" width="190" height="215" alt=""/></span></p>
        <p align="center" class="style1871"><em>Earlier American Composers: Survey in Sound</em></p>
        <p align="center" class="style183">A selection of  vocal and instrumental music <br>
          by 16 composers
        from 1759 to 1919</p>
